Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Japan of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's a small country, but the climate in the north is quite different from the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amaimon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that the Infinity Key is not for sightsee{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha-That's the Honey-Honey Sisters yukata that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,counts as a rare item even in the holy lands!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just queued and bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the true Japanese{,} samurai spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the wonderful world of moe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having such a great little brother fills my heart with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Brother, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you finally feel like playing a bit with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather bring a date to the amusement park after school, not come here like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was your team's last mission, Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sure if you could call it a mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a huge squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, that's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there are people who are not even doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi, what happened? Your kimono...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:04:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kimono's not fit for missions, so the Principal assigned me a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're late because Kamiki had to show me how to put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too weird I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, it's good, it's hella cute, Moriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that skirt a bit too short? Huh, Yukio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You were checking out her boo{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, four-eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're all here, let me assign you in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa, Takara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, Suguro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiki, Shima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura, Moriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:05:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately we've been getting sightings of a ghost and reports of damage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,here in MepphyLand, so today you'll investigate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to find it today while the park is closed to public,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as soon as you do, report to either professor Tsubaki's or my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can someone please define what is a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Ghosts are demons that possess vapors emitted from the corpses of humans or animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They often exhibit residual emotions from the lifetime of the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many ghosts are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one, although there have been sightings from all around the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes the appearance of a small boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It usually does nothing more than pulling hands or lifting skirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Lifting skirts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are childish pranks. Then again, it is a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we leave it be, there's a danger of it becoming more vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be easy with this many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin, you watch the right side. I'll watch this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really suits her well. Wait, isn't this... like a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi? What's wrong? What happened to your face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm... Not laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to go to the amusement park,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't stand so many people around me, so it was out of the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's normally crowded and a lot of fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's come here together next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then let's decide where we should look next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Rin! How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't talk to demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's tiny and he doesn't look dangerous at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How long do you want to keep on crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't yell at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very sick... But my parents promised me we'd come here when I get well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I died, so no one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you were just lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat! I wanted to rub{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that pervy brat go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin, I'll check over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! That kid... What does he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah right, I should report that we found him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Amaimon, a demon king. Kinda like your big brother. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm not giving this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Demon-Slaying Blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{CM}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it hurt to help me look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So the sword is connected to Gehenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the scabbard is the gate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the sword is sheathed the gate closes, and when it's drawn it opens again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, make up your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's leave it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your flames are in Gehenna, and your body is in Assiah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to our brother's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I want? I had some free time so I came here to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an amusement park after all, so let's have a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura! Did you turn the electricity on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see anything from where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I studied Japanese games as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little... don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hag, wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad! Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to go to the amusement park...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Such a bad boy! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me, I went to the seaside the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surfing's so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned about this game, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't look like a ghost to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it... Why are Father and Brother so obsessed with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a let down. I hoped you'd be good for killing some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It's like in a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playtime's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing at? We could've died!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very sick, so I never played outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever scolded me or picked me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is it over already? So boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother's been holding me back, but I'm thinking I should break your sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sever the head of the snake that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,devours the eight princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Amaimon, the Earth King, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could a big fish like you get inside the Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mephisto let you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the one in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, screw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People will be here soon. Hide your tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took my sword so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost it for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no different from back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared. He said "thanks, sis."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin! We should totally come here together next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, Rin is wounded, he needs help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What took you so long? I had to make my move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fed up with this look anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:22:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vatican Headquarters dispatched me to investigate risk factors in the Japanese Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shura Kirigakure, High Inspector, Upper First Class Exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{3}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been hiding the existence of Satan's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.22,0:23:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I haven't been hiding him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.42,0:24:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all for the sake of the Order of the True Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to believe in you, Shiro.
