Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:44.55,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,sei wo uke sorezore ga jinsei wo ouka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:47.18,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,nou no black box wo shiru sore wa kou ka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:49.73,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,you wa limit line wo subete ryouga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:52.69,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,saa ikou ka fumidasu sore wa kyou da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:57.98,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,yappa hibi wa ika sen kou sotsunaku konashitecha no no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:03.11,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,stop nagare wo mikiwamena mazu mono to mo sezu ikou ze (here we go)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:07.87,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,todokanu mono ya kagiri aru mono ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.46,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,atsuku naru mune wo osaetsukeru no wa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:17.97,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,rikai mo sezu osaetsukeyou to shitekita
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:21.84,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,ano otonatachi to onaji jan ka yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:26.93,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,doushitatte kanawanai esoragoto darou ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:31.43,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mune wo moyasu hi wa dare ni mo keseya shinai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:36.69,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,sora kara furu kuroi ame ga kono mi nurashi furitomanakutomo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:42.11,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mada ore wa kawareru jibun de kaetemiseru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:47.58,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}kore ga sou "pride" sorezore no basho de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:51.91,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,717)}mada mada kieru na kokoro no hi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:57.38,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mada mada ikeru zo ikeru zo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:44.55,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,After birth, people live as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:47.18,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,They then learn the black box in their head; is that bliss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:49.73,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cross over, beyond the line of your limit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:52.69,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, take a step, and I mean this minute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:57.98,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Life's a bitch, so if it's easy, you're doing it wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:03.11,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, which way is the world going? Then ignore it and go wherever (here we go)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:07.87,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I could never have, things with time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.46,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason I force my heart upon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:17.97,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I never tried to understand, I just forced it on them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:21.84,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no better than those lifeless adults
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:26.93,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just a pipe dream I could never have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:31.43,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one can put out the fire in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:36.69,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The black rain may pour hard and leave me drenched
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:42.11,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know I can change, I will change myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:47.58,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}This is my pride, what makes up my core
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:51.91,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,15)}I won't let my fire be put out; not yet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:57.38,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep going, and I'll never stop
